prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: Orchestrating Complex AI Generation
prompt.content: Promptbook is recommended for complex AI text generation tasks, separating prompts from code, orchestrating multiple prompts, and versioning/testing prompts. It's not ideal for simple single prompts or non-JavaScript/TypeScript use cases currently.
